  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/7eeb66bdfb9baa33264dfe736fafbb74.poster.avif?t=1773751683\" width=780 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/7eeb66bdfb9baa33264dfe736fafbb74.webm?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/7eeb66bdfb9baa33264dfe736fafbb74.mp4?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TYPE. UPGRADE. OVERCOME.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KeyBreach</strong> is not a typing tutor, it’s a survival test. You are an operator breaching a hostile mainframe. The security protocols are getting faster, the viruses are getting smarter, and your only defense is your WPM (Words Per Minute) and your ability to exploit the system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/59414c88975fd15a69b4f0ed84399aa5.poster.avif?t=1773751683\" width=780 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/59414c88975fd15a69b4f0ed84399aa5.webm?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/59414c88975fd15a69b4f0ed84399aa5.mp4?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR OPERATOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You aren't just a cursor. Choose from <strong>5 distinct characters</strong>, each with unique skill trees and playstyles:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE BROKER:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Playstyle:</i> Economy & Tanking.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE EXPLOIT:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Playstyle:</i> High Risk & Forgiveness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE GLITCHER:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Playstyle:</i> Chaos & RNG.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE SAVIOR:</strong><br>Playstyle: Defense & Blessings.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE PERFECT:</strong><br>Playstyle: Precision & Momentum.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/59ddc672b630ca15b31fe778bd4414b3.poster.avif?t=1773751683\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/59ddc672b630ca15b31fe778bd4414b3.webm?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/59ddc672b630ca15b31fe778bd4414b3.mp4?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMPILE YOUR CODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed alone won't save you. You need a build.<br>Combine over <strong>100+ Items</strong> to create game-breaking synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/4f0b27e22c74e0f3a33576f3be2e552a.poster.avif?t=1773751683\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/4f0b27e22c74e0f3a33576f3be2e552a.webm?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300620/extras/4f0b27e22c74e0f3a33576f3be2e552a.mp4?t=1773751683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TERMINAL FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>25+ Unique Boss Encounters:</strong> This isn't just typing faster. You must survive specific boss mechanics—<strong>The Firewall</strong> blocks your input, <strong>The Ransomware King</strong> steals your gold, and <strong>The Shapeshifter</strong> changes words mid-fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+ Unlockable Interfaces:</strong> Customize your workspace. Switch between <i>Matrix Green</i>, <i>Retro Amber</i>, <i>Vaporwave</i>, or induce anxiety with the <i>Blue Screen of Death</i> theme.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Replayability:</strong> A true Roguelike loop. No two runs are the same as you draft from a pool of 100+ items, managing economy, time, and sanity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real-Life Debuffs:</strong> Hand cramps and Carpal Tunnel Syndrome included at no extra charge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The system is waiting. Do you have what it takes to reach Root Access?</strong></p>",
